00:07:55.973 --> 00:07:58.493
were either wholeheartedly with

00:07:58.730 --> 00:08:00.683
MBS’s plan for the new Saudi

00:08:00.683 --> 00:08:02.903
Arabia, or you were against it.

00:08:04.633 --> 00:08:08.003
